        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带爷的枪马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四文堂、四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "人来带过少爷的马，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "阵前去会佘赛花。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（佘赛花、四文堂、四女兵、女马童同上，打过合。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "阵前来了杨家将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由奴家怒胸膛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "少时教你无下场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "（佘赛花、四文堂、四女兵、女马童、杨继业、四文堂、四上手同钻烟筒下，杨继业、佘赛花同上，同起打，"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "杨继业败下，佘赛花耍枪花下。四上手、四女兵同上，同起打，双下。杨继业败上，佘赛花追上，同起打，"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "杨继业败下，佘赛花追下。杨继业上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "提枪拍马往前闯"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！看这个丫头杀法厉害，杀得我上天无路，入地无门，这便如何是好！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七星庙，七星庙！来此已是七星庙，待我下马进庙。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业下马，进庙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我将门闭上，在此处躲避一时，再作道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（佘赛花上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！适才与杨家小将交战，被奴将他杀得大败，他在前面跑，奴在后面赶，来"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在此地，为何不见？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（佘赛花看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "七星庙，七星庙！想是他在庙中藏躲，看他将庙门关闭，这便怎么处？待奴喊"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！杨家小将听着：你家姑娘在此等候，你快开庙门，与姑娘再战三合！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个丫头，她竟自赶来了！她叫我开门与她再战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你家少爷在庙内安身，任凭你这丫头说得天花乱坠，你少爷就是不开门的了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看他执意不肯开门，这便如何是好？哦哦有啦，待我吓他一吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨家小将，你隐藏庙内，不肯开门，待奴吩咐三军，将庙墙团团围住，四面放"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起火来，将庙宇烧坏，管叫你死无葬身之地！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，这个丫头言道：吩咐三军，将庙宇烧坏，要叫我死无葬身之地，这便怎"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业跪拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望求神圣保佑，望求神圣保佑！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，佘赛花丫头，既叫你少爷开门，你少爷敢开庙门，只怕你不敢下马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你既敢开庙门，你姑娘就敢下马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业跪拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望求神圣多多保佑！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你姑娘下马来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我与你开门！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你开来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业开门，佘赛花执枪刺杨继业，杨继业夺枪，绑佘赛花跪地。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看你这丫头，还往哪里走！待我将她的战马，牵进庙来，将庙门关闭了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业拴马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好杀呀好杀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好战哪好战！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好跑哇好跑！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好赶哪好赶！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赶的你家少爷是燕儿不下蛋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赶的你姑娘是一身的透汗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这丫头，实实的好狠心哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你的心肠也就不软！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得你少爷心狠？"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你为何将奴家兄长杀死？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就不该赖了我的亲事！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是我爹爹做主，与奴什么相干？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你倒推得干净！今日你既被擒，我且问你：你是愿意一死，还是愿意一活？"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "死是怎样讲，活是怎么说？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要是愿意死呀，我就是这一枪，将你刺死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这一活呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这一活么？来来来，你就与我成亲事、拜天地！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我呀，我愿意一死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个丫头她愿意一死！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业提枪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，你看枪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（佘赛花闪开。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来！我愿意一活。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你愿意一活？好好好，来来来，拜天地吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看世界之上，哪有捆着绑着拜天地的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是想叫我与你松绑啊？"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是自然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我要与你松了绑，怕你一时反悔，你须要与我对天盟誓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我一生一世，就是不会盟誓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你既不会盟誓，你还是与我一死吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨继业倒提枪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，看枪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我盟誓，我盟誓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不要害怕，你看这是枪把，枪头儿在这一头儿呢。你与我盟誓吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇天在上，我佘赛花在下，我今与小将成亲，若有三心二意，天厌之，天厌之！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么叫做“添胭脂”？你还要添粉不成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃是个咒语。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是一句咒语！待我与你松绑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看今日在庙内，你我夫妻何处安身？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有何难？你我就将马褥子拿下来，铺在殿内，就此成亲便了。你我来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（佘赛花欲拔剑砍杨继业，杨继业退。小过门。杨继业比手势要佘赛花拜天地，佘赛花羞，宝剑入鞘。杨继"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "业暗拔佘赛花宝剑，以剑砍佘赛花，佘赛花急拔剑，见剑被杨继业拔去，向杨继业讨剑，杨继业比手势要佘"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赛花拜天地。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我就此一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（佘赛花、杨继业同拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二人庙内双跪定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "佘赛花",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "夫妻双双把亲成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨继业",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "先拜天地与神灵，"
        },
        {
